      <p>(d) Therefore, no Guarantor shall, in particular but without limitation, be entitled to challenge any demand of payment under this Guarantee Agreement nor raise any objection, defence, exception, deduction, withholding, lien, right of<nobr>set-off</nobr> or counterclaim resulting from or related to:</p>
      <p>(i) any provisions governing a Transaction;</p>
