      <p>Proceeds mean any interest, fees, profits, and Recoveries received under the underlying transactions and, for equity transactions, any reflows (including restitution of commitment and distributions).</p>
      <p>Recoveries means moneys recovered from underlying transactions.</p>
      <p>Proceeds and Recoveries received under an operation of the Fund shall be allocated by the Bank acting on the account of the Fund at the end of each quarter 31 March, 30 June, 30 September, 31 December between the Contributors and the EIB and EIF as follows:</p>
