      <p>
        <nobr>COVID-19</nobr> crisis. However, a number of companies are already very strongly affected</p>
      <p>and will continue to be impacted in the<nobr>short-term.</nobr> Due to specifics of the VC/PE</p>
      <p>industry, these companies require dedicated and<nobr>tailor-made</nobr>
        <nobr>equity-like</nobr> support.</p>
