      <p>operating in the EU Member States.</p>
      <p>TUF is expected to finance predominantly portfolio companies: i) to overcome short</p>
      <p>and<nobr>mid-term</nobr> liquidity constrains resulting from loss of revenue, ii) to increase</p>
      <p>production capacity, and iii) to finance market or product development.</p>
      <p>In terms of stage, the facility is expected to focus more prominently on one or more of the stages listed below:</p>
      <p>☒<nobr>Pre-seed /</nobr> Seed</p>
