      <p>(x) proposing amendments to the provisions of the Platform Rules, in consultation with Contributors, where appropriate;</p>
      <p>(xi) supporting each Contributors’ Committee in commissioning reviews and evaluations;</p>
      <p>(xii) ensuring that, in communicating internally and externally, in its publications, in communication with beneficiaries, countries and other entities as well as the media, appropriate visibility is given to the Platform and its Contributors;</p>
